  "original_title": "Businesses with multiple vehicles can register with National Fuel Pass portal",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Businesses with multiple vehicles can register with National Fuel Pass portal",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Businesses with large fleet of vehicles can now register all their vehicles with their Business Registration Number on the National Fuel Pass (NFP), Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wiesekera said.",
        "He said the system upgrades were made considering the issues received by the Ministry during the trial period on registering with the portal.",
        "Accordingly, the NFP portal was upgraded to give an option for businesses and organizations that operate with more than one vehicle\u00a0 to register all their vehicles with the Business Registration Number.",
        "Such vehicles will be given a specific QR code through the portal after verification.",
        "Moreover, he said that the fuel requirements for machinery must be registered with the respective Divisonal Secretariats with the weekly fuel requirements. (Chatuanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
